msgid "Raises"
msgstr ""

#: chaotic_pfc.analysis.sweep_plotting.plot_difficulty_map:19 of
msgid ""
"If ``result`` was produced with ``adaptive=False`` (the heatmap     would"
" be a single colour, which is misleading rather than     informative). "
"The error message points the user to the     ``adaptive=True`` flag in "
":func:`run_sweep`."
msgstr ""

#: chaotic_pfc.analysis.sweep_plotting.plot_all:1 of
